<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en" data-theme="light"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="cid:css-fbb79263-cf73-47c7-951d-3b969a4e82e5@mhtml.blink" />

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#01696f">
<title>Sleep Diary</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com/" crossorigin="">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=DM+Serif+Display&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>
<div class="top"><div class="topin"><div class="brand"><div class="logo" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3c4.5 0 8 2.7 9 6-4.2-.7-7.1.3-9 2.8C10.1 9.3 7.2 8.3 3 9c1-3.3 4.5-6 9-6z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="15.5" r="4.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle></svg></div><div><div class="title">Sleep Diary</div><div class="sub">CBT-I plan · 6:00 am wake time</div></div></div><button class="iconbtn" id="themeBtn" aria-label="Toggle theme">◐</button></div></div>
<div class="wrap">
<section class="hero"><div class="eyebrow">Phone-friendly · saves on your device</div><h1>Morning sleep diary.</h1><p>Fill this in within an hour of getting up. Entries are saved in your browser on your device when hosted on a normal website like GitHub Pages.</p></section>
<div class="tabs">
<button class="tab active" data-tab="log">Log today</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="history">History</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="rules">Rules</button>
<button class="tab" data-tab="schedule">Schedule</button>
</div>
<section class="panel active" id="panel-log">
<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Sleep timing</h2></div>
<div class="fields">
<div><label class="label" for="date">Date</label><input class="input" id="date" type="date"></div>
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="bed">Got into bed</label><input class="input" id="bed" type="time"></div>
<div><label class="label" for="trySleep">Tried to sleep</label><input class="input" id="trySleep" type="time"></div>
</div>
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="sleepLatency">Minutes to fall asleep</label><input class="input" id="sleepLatency" type="number" min="0" max="300" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="20"></div>
<div><label class="label" for="finalWake">Final wake-up time</label><input class="input" id="finalWake" type="time" value="06:00"></div>
</div>
<div><label class="label" for="outBed">Out of bed time</label><input class="input" id="outBed" type="time" value="06:00"><div class="hint">Your fixed wake time is 6:00 am.</div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Night awakenings</h2></div>
<div class="fields">
<div><label class="label">How many awakenings?</label><div class="counter"><button type="button" class="countbtn" id="minus">−</button><div class="count" id="wakeCount">0</div><button type="button" class="countbtn" id="plus">+</button></div></div>
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="awakeMinutes">Total minutes awake overnight</label><input class="input" id="awakeMinutes" type="number" min="0" max="600" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="30"></div>
<div><label class="label" for="gotUp">Got out of bed if awake?</label><select class="select" id="gotUp"><option value="">Select</option><option>Yes</option><option>No, awake under 15 min</option><option>No, stayed in bed too long</option><option>Not applicable</option></select></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Day factors</h2></div>
<div class="fields">
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="nap">Nap yesterday</label><select class="select" id="nap"><option>No nap</option><option>Short nap under 20 min</option><option>Long nap 20 min+</option></select></div>
<div><label class="label" for="caffeine">Last caffeine time</label><input class="input" id="caffeine" type="time"></div>
</div>
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="alcohol">Alcohol</label><select class="select" id="alcohol"><option>None</option><option>1 drink</option><option>2+ drinks</option></select></div>
<div><label class="label" for="exercise">Exercise</label><select class="select" id="exercise"><option>None</option><option>Light</option><option>Moderate</option><option>Vigorous</option></select></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Sleep quality</h2></div>
<div class="fields">
<div><label class="label">How did it feel?</label><div class="stars" id="stars"><button type="button" class="star" data-star="1">⭐</button><button type="button" class="star" data-star="2">⭐</button><button type="button" class="star" data-star="3">⭐</button><button type="button" class="star" data-star="4">⭐</button><button type="button" class="star" data-star="5">⭐</button></div><div class="hint" id="starText">Tap a star to rate last night.</div></div>
<div class="two">
<div><label class="label" for="mood">Morning energy</label><select class="select" id="mood"><option value="">Select</option><option>Refreshed</option><option>Okay</option><option>Tired</option><option>Exhausted</option></select></div>
<div><label class="label" for="sleepy">Sleepy at bedtime?</label><select class="select" id="sleepy"><option value="">Select</option><option>Yes</option><option>A bit</option><option>No</option></select></div>
</div>
<div><label class="label" for="notes">Notes</label><textarea class="area" id="notes" placeholder="Stress, illness, travel, unusual events, or anything worth noting."></textarea></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="notice">Tip: fill this in within an hour of getting up. Estimates are fine — the pattern matters more than exact precision.</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="panel" id="panel-history"><div class="card"><div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Your entries</h2></div><div id="history"><div class="empty">No entries yet. Save your first morning log and it will appear here.</div></div></div></section>
<section class="panel" id="panel-rules"><div class="card"><div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Daily CBT-I rules</h2></div><div class="row"><div><strong>Wake at 6:00 am every day</strong><span>No sleeping in after a bad night.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>Do not go to bed before 11:30 pm</strong><span>Only go to bed when you feel sleepy.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>If awake 15–20 minutes, get out of bed</strong><span>Go somewhere dim and calm, then return when sleepy.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>No naps for now</strong><span>They weaken sleep drive at night.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>Stop caffeine by around 2 pm</strong><span>Late caffeine can push sleep later.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>Bed is only for sleep and sex</strong><span>No doomscrolling, work, or TV in bed.</span></div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>Do not clock-watch</strong><span>Checking time increases pressure and frustration.</span></div></div></div></section>
<section class="panel" id="panel-schedule"><div class="card"><div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Evening wind-down</h2></div><div class="row"><div><strong>9:15 pm</strong><span>Dim lights and stop work.</span></div><div class="time">9:15</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>9:25 pm</strong><span>Shower or wash up.</span></div><div class="time">9:25</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>9:35 pm</strong><span>Ten minutes of slow breathing or muscle relaxation.</span></div><div class="time">9:35</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>9:45 pm</strong><span>Quiet reading or calm audio.</span></div><div class="time">9:45</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>10:30 pm</strong><span>Write down worries or tomorrow's tasks so they are out of your head.</span></div><div class="time">10:30</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>11:30 pm</strong><span>Go to bed only if sleepy.</span></div><div class="time">11:30</div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="sectionhead"><div class="dot"></div><h2>Morning routine (6:00 am wake)</h2></div><div class="row"><div><strong>6:00 am</strong><span>Get up at the alarm, even after a rough night.</span></div><div class="time">6:00</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>6:05 am</strong><span>Get daylight fast if you can.</span></div><div class="time">6:05</div></div><div class="row"><div><strong>6:15 am</strong><span>Fill in your diary.</span></div><div class="time">6:15</div></div></div></section>
</div>
<div class="footerbar"><div class="inner"><button id="saveBtn" class="primary">Save today's entry</button></div></div>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>


</body></html>
